---
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
  <title>About | Clinic Flow Studio</title>

  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@500&family=Inter:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Inter, sans-serif;
      background: #f6f1e7;
      color: #2f3a2f;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }

    h1, h2 {
      font-family: "Playfair Display", serif;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 850px;
      margin: auto;
      padding: 80px 20px;
    }

    .card {
      background: white;
      padding: 50px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    }

    .etsy-button {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding: 14px 26px;
      background: #4f6b4f;
      color: white;
      border-radius: 10px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <Header />

  <div class="container">

    <div class="card">

      <h1>About Me</h1>

      <p>
        I created this shop to help veterinary professionals stay organized,
        save time, and make clinic life feel a little less overwhelming.
      </p>

      <p>
        As someone passionate about veterinary medicine and efficient workflows,
        I know how busy things can get behind the scenes —
        from patient care and paperwork to keeping the entire day running smoothly.
      </p>

      <p>
        That’s why I design clean, practical, and easy-to-use digital templates
        made specifically for vet clinics, vet techs, assistants,
        students, and pet care teams.
      </p>

      <p>
        Whether you’re looking for printable forms,
        editable clinic templates, workflow tools,
        or organization trackers,
        my goal is to make your daily routine easier and more organized.
      </p>

      <h2>Outside the Clinic</h2>

      <p>
        When I’m not designing templates,
        I spend time with my pets — Juno, Luna, Sushi, and Sriracha.
      </p>

      <p>
        I also love reading, hiking, painting,
        and watching horror movies.
        Creativity and calm balance inspire both my life and my work.
      </p>

      <p>
        Everything in my shop is created with care,
        simplicity, and real clinic life in mind.
      </p>

      <p>
        Thank you so much for supporting my small business —
        I’m so happy you’re here!
      </p>

      <a class="etsy-button"
         href="https://www.etsy.com/shop/ClinicFlowStudioCo">
        Visit My Etsy Shop
      </a>

    </div>

  </div>

  <Footer />

</body>
</html>
